abstract: Brit blacklist of enemy interests in neutral countries revised; list
snippet: England's "blacklist" of companies operated by "enemy" interests in neutral countries has been increased by the addition of seventyfive new names, according to copies of the latest amendment reaching here from England....

headline.main: ENGLAND EXPANDS TRADE 'BLACKLIST'; Adds 75 Companies to Those Already Cited as 'Enemies' in Neutral Nations FOR NAMES ARE DELETED Corrections Are Made in Other Listings--No U.S. Concern Is Included

lead_paragraph: England's "blacklist" of companies operated by "enemy" interests in neutral countries has been increased by the addition of seventyfive new names, according to copies of the latest amendment reaching here from England.
